latestPosts.caption:
You have survived too many storms 
to be bothered by raindrops. 

If you see my life from a distance it’s all rosy and beautiful, 
but the reality changes everyday…

Sometimes health, kids, daily chores, unpleasant incidents, seeing to different faces of the same old person forces you to think. 

Who is even left honest and genuine in this world ?  You deal with fake appreciation, work pressures, politics be it at work or within relationships. 

You deal with 100 red flags everyday.

Only you know your struggles of not able to loose weight. Or not able to gain weight people say you look pale and weak no outfit suits you.

Social media is one such myth where you see people sipping their coffees in a clean house with humming songs on Alexa.

I don’t even get time to arrange my cupboard and here you see people doing everything perfect. Believe be behind the lens their house helps arrange and complete their work and you think yaar Kitni perfect hai iski life.

So don’t just make a perception on what you see online. Half of it is made up to show off.

I love spring and flowers while driving back my daughter from her play date I saw these beautiful bougainvilleas could not resist myself from getting clicked. 

But mind you only I know how much I had to plead and bribe my daughter to get these few clicks🤣 

#thingsidoinmotherhood #thingsidoforlove #bougainvillea #springvibes🌸 #pinks

latestPosts.caption:
Hope isn’t just a word it’s a belief that one day everything will fall in place🧿 Hope is a string that ties us to God whom we look up to when left with no option.
But truth is there’s always an option, a way, a solution, an angle in disguise. We only need to find ours.

I hope you heal from the trauma 
you never got an apology for……….

I hope you find peace 
with all that is unsettled in your heart……….

I hope you find serenity 
in a world you may not always understand……….

I hope one day you meet someone 
who makes you feel safe enough to rediscover that softer version of yourself…………

I hope eventually all waves settle and you reach the shore……….
